William Farnum https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Farnum 0 William Farnum (July 4, 1876 – June 5, 1953) was an American stage and film actor. He was a star of American silent film cinema and became one of the highest-paid actors during that time. William_Farnum ( July_4_,_1876 – June_5_,_1953 ) was an_American_stage_and_film_actor .
